<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q8_v8" title="Q8_v8" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>Registro del caso:</p><p>
      En un stand de limonada de una feria escolar se preparará una bebida mezclando bebida gaseosa y jugo de limón para servir en 
      <m:math><m:mn>180</m:mn></m:math>
      vasos.
    </p>
    <p>
      La siguiente ficha muestra las cantidades de ingredientes necesarias por vaso:
      <br />Ficha de preparación por vaso:
      <br />- Bebida gaseosa: 2 onzas por vaso
      <br />- Jugo de limón: 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mspace width="0.2em" />
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      onzas por vaso
      <br />
      <br />Recordar: 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mtext> onza</m:mtext>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>30</m:mn>
          <m:mtext> mL</m:mtext>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>.
      <br />
      <br />¿Cuántos mL de jugo de limón se necesitan en total para preparar los 180 vasos?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">270 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El jugo de limón por vaso es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Para <m:math><m:mn>180</m:mn></m:math> vasos se necesita <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>270</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas, no <m:math><m:mn>270</m:mn></m:math> mL. Luego, como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> onza</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>270</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8&#160;100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">8 100 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Cada vaso usa <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jugo de limón. Para <m:math><m:mn>180</m:mn></m:math> vasos: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>270</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> onza</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>270</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8&#160;100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">2700 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El total de jugo de limón en onzas es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>270</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Al convertir a mililitros se debe multiplicar por <m:math><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math>: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>270</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8&#160;100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>2&#160;700</m:mn></m:math> mL no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">18 900 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La cantidad de jugo de limón por vaso es solo <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Entonces, para <m:math><m:mn>180</m:mn></m:math> vasos se requieren <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>270</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Convirtiendo: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>270</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8&#160;100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL. Por eso, <m:math><m:mn>18&#160;900</m:mn></m:math> mL es mayor que el total necesario y no corresponde.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Identificar la cantidad de jugo de limón por vaso</strong></p>
            <p>La ficha indica que cada vaso lleva <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jugo de limón.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular las onzas totales para 180 vasos</strong></p>
            <p>Multiplicamos la cantidad por vaso por la cantidad de vasos:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>270</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Convertir onzas a mililitros</strong></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> onza</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>270</m:mn><m:mtext> onzas</m:mtext><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8&#160;100</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>Se necesitan <m:math><m:mn>8&#160;100</m:mn></m:math> mL de jugo de limón en total.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>